API which we are gonna use :-

1>A single coin API.
2>A coin list API.
3>A historical chart displaying API.
4>API for displaying some trending Coins.

Package Installations :-

npm install @material-ui/core
npm install @material-ui/lab
npm install react-router-dom
npm i axios 
npm i react-html-parser removed this library for parsing the description in CoinPage .
npm i html-react-parser instead of above library used this one .

Issue faced in CoinInfo page that is when fetch the desription property from the APIÂ  encountered a issue that , it is containing anchor tag inside the desription So I have make use of a package i.e react-html-parser package which will parse the description & display the proper description in normal text.

